  <h3>The Basics</h3>
  <h4>Tips for Kids</h4>
  <hr>
  <div class="group">
   <div class="circ-num">
    <span>1</span>
   </div> <img class="col5" src="../img/resilience_tipkid_1.png" alt="Baby Kate cries.">
   <div class="col7">
    <p>You might have heard about something upsetting that happened near you or far away. Sometimes these kinds of events can make you feel sad, unhappy, or afraid. Remember that it's okay to feel upset if you hear about or experience a scary situation. You might want to cry or feel like you can't settle down.</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="group">
   <div class="circ-num">
    <span>2</span>
   </div> <img class="col5" src="../img/resilience_tipkid_2.png" alt="Mr. Ratburn holds a book and gestures.">
   <div class="col7">
    <p>If you feel scared or worried, talk to a grown-up, such as a parent, grandparent, or teacher.</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="group">
   <div class="circ-num">
    <span>3</span>
   </div> <img class="col5" src="../img/resilience_tipkid_3.png" alt="Arthur hugs his dad.">
   <div class="col7">
    <p>Are your feelings making it hard to eat, sleep, or play? The grown-ups in your life are there to help you feel better.</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="group">
   <div class="circ-num">
    <span>4</span>
   </div> <img class="col5" src="../img/resilience_tipkid_4.png" alt="Blue stuffed bunny.">
   <div class="col7">
    <p>You may want to cuddle up with your favorite stuffed animal, even one you haven't used in a while. That's okay, too.</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="group">
   <div class="circ-num">
    <span>5</span>
   </div> <img class="col5" src="../img/resilience_tipkid_5.png" alt="Binky and Brain read together.">
   <div class="col7">
    <p>If you have a friend who is upset by something that happened to him or her, you may wonder what you should do or say. You can be a good friend by just offering to spend time together.</p>
   </div>
